divs: Sighting DetailsSighting Report: Time 10:45-10:50 pm appox. seen bright light flying across sky as i looked out my bedroom window noticed it because it was going so fast must faster than a plane or coppter. my window faces directly west object was at a 10 o clock position when i first say it was out of view within 5-7 seconds going in a easterly direction and was just to my left which would be south. can not say it was a UFO so to speak- But was not a plane nor coppter. please do not contact me about this unless there has been other sightings.this is just for your information only also the night was clear and cold temps in the teens.. thanks
